Top 7 places to visit in Mysore:
	1.	Mysore Palace – Grand royal palace with stunning architecture and evening lighting.
	2.	Chamundi Hill & Chamundeshwari Temple – Sacred hill with a revered temple and city views.
	3.	Brindavan Gardens – Famous for its musical fountain and beautiful landscaping.
	4.	Mysore Zoo – One of India’s best zoos, home to a wide variety of animals.
	5.	St. Philomena’s Church – Impressive neo-gothic cathedral with towering spires.
	6.	Jaganmohan Palace & Art Gallery – Historic site housing classical paintings and artifacts.
	7.	Ranganathittu Bird Sanctuary – Peaceful birding spot with boat rides and exotic birds.
